<P>ACTS AND LAWS, Pa&s;&s;ed by the Great and General Court or A&s;&s;embly of His Maje&s;ties Province of the Ma&s;&s;achu&s;etts-Bay, in New-England.</P>
<P>Begun and Held at <HI>Boston</HI> the Twenty-fifth Day of <HI>May,</HI> 1698. and continued by Prorogation until <HI>Tue&s;day</HI> the Fifteenth of <HI>November</HI> following: being the Second Se&s;&s;ion.</P>
<P>Anno Regni <HI>Guilielmi</HI> Tertii, Angliae, Scotiae, Franciae, et Hiberniae, REGIS, <HI>Decimo.</HI></P>
<P><FIGURE>
</FIGURE></P>
<P>BOSTON, Printed by <HI>Bartholomew Green,</HI> and <HI>John Allen,</HI> Printers to the <HI>Governour</HI> and <HI>Council.</HI> 1698.</P>
</DIV1>
